graph TB
    subgraph Controller["ModelMesh Serving Controller"]
        direction TB
        MC[modelmesh-controller<br/>Go Operator<br/>controller-runtime]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        MC -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph RuntimePod["Runtime Pod (per ServingRuntime)"]
        direction TB
        MM[ModelMesh Container<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>HTTP 8008/TCP]
        OAuthProxy[oauth-proxy<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP]
        Puller[Storage Puller<br/>gRPC 8086/TCP]
        RuntimeContainer[Model Runtime<br/>Triton/MLServer/OVMS/TorchServe]

        OAuthProxy -->|proxies to| RESTProxy
        RESTProxy -->|translates REST to gRPC| MM
        MM -->|inference via UDS/TCP| RuntimeContainer
        Puller -->|downloads models to| RuntimeContainer
    end

    User[Data Scientist / Client] -->|creates| PredictorCR[Predictor CR]
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR]
    User -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>optional]

    PredictorCR -->|watched by| MC
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| MC
    InferenceServiceCR -->|converted to Predictor by| MC

    MC -->|creates/manages| RuntimePod
    MC -->|registers models via gRPC| MM
    MC -->|creates| HPAs[HorizontalPodAutoscaler]
    MC -->|creates| Services[modelmesh-serving Service<br/>headless ClusterIP]

    MM -->|state sync| etcd[etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP]
    MC -->|watches events| etcd

    Puller -->|downloads from| ObjectStorage[Object Storage<br/>S3 / GCS / Azure / PVC]

    style MC fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style MM fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style RESTProxy fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style OAuthProxy fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style Puller fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style RuntimeContainer fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style etcd fill:#e8e8e8,color:#333
    style ObjectStorage fill:#e8e8e8,color:#333
    style HPAs fill:#ddd,color:#333
    style Services fill:#ddd,color:#333
